<li>Jennings, A., et al. (2018). “<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6134287/">A Mediterranean-like dietary pattern with vitamin D3 (10 microg/d) supplements reduced the rate of bone loss in older Europeans with osteoporosis at baseline: results of a 1-y randomized controlled trial.</a>" Am J Clin Nutr 108(3): 633-640.</li>
