<li>Filomeno, M., et al. (2015). “<a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1038/bjc.2015.153">Mediterranean diet and risk of endometrial cancer: a pooled analysis of three Italian case-control studies.</a>" Br J Cancer 112(11): 1816-1821</li>
