<li><a href="http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2013/05/130520154303.htm">Ohio State University. (2013, May 20). Compound in Mediterranean diet makes cancer cells ‘mortal’. ScienceDaily. Retrieved February 24, 2020</a></li>
